invalid type: string "# SECTION: Muscle Building Strategy\n\n## Summary\nMuscle growth requires resistance training, proper nutrition, and recovery.\n\n## Key Principles\n- progressive overload\n- sufficient protein intake\n- adequate rest\n\n## Example Routine\n- train each muscle group 2 times per week\n\n## Nutrition\n- protein intake: 1.6–2.2g per kg body weight\n\n## Risks\n- overtraining\n